<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="un6009f"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="un6" href="#un6009">UN6: </a>  <a href="../../ff/unbs/un6all.htm#un6009f"> (NLI.4) 9(f)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Chas Hart actor WS&apos;s grandnephew, </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: Charles Hart (1625-1683) fought in the battle of Edge-hill, as lieutenant, in Prince Rupert&apos;s regiment, and afterwards became a very celebrated tragic actor of the restoration period. He is believed (falsely) to have been the grandson of Shakespeare&apos;s sister Jon, the wife of William Hart, a hatter in Stratford.  <br>Raphael transcription: <a name="c07236h" href="../../../f/ff/fnbs/c07all.htm#c07236h">VI.C.07:236(h)</a> </mm></dd> </dd></dl>
